'''柯马提鱼屬'''（[[學名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Cometicercus''}}，意為「[[彗星|彗星]]般的尾部」）是一种已灭绝的[[花鳞鱼纲|花鳞鱼纲]]魚類，生存于[[泥盆纪|泥盆纪]]早期的[[加拿大|加拿大]][[西北地方_(加拿大)|西北地方]] ，可由它似尾部的鰭及背部表觀（如背鰭）辨認出來<ref name = "Wilson">{{cite journal | author = M. V. H. Wilson, M. W. Caldwell | year = 1998 | title = "The Furcacaudiformes: a new order of jawless vertebrates with thelodont scales, based on articulated Silurian and Devonian fossils from northern Canada" | journal = ''Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology'' | volume = 18 | number = 1 | pages = 10–29 | doi = 10.1080/02724634.1998.10011031 }}</ref>。

